# Rules Location

All Cursor rules must be:
- Located in the `.cursor/rules` directory
- Named with the `.mdc` extension
- Follow kebab-case naming convention
- Each rule should be in its own file
- Rules should be clear and concise
- Rules should be categorized by their purpose (e.g., performance, security, coding-standards) 